                </div>
                <div class="info-box-text">
                    黃頷蛇科，<a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.probertencyclopaedia.com/B_LYCODONTINAE.HTM" lang="en-US">Lycodontinae</a> 亞科
                    <br>
                    <span lang="en-US">Colubridae, subfamily <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://www.probertencyclopaedia.com/B_LYCODONTINAE.HTM">Lycodontinae</a></span> 
